### Discord-Specific Utilities

**USE**: `discord.tsx` from `@utils/discord`

**Available functions:**
- `getIntlMessage(key, values?)` - Get internationalized message
- `getIntlMessageFromHash(hashedKey, values?, originalKey?)` - Get i18n from hash
- `openInviteModal(code)` - Open invite modal
- `getCurrentChannel()` - Get current channel
- `getCurrentGuild()` - Get current guild
- `openPrivateChannel(userId)` - Open DM channel
- `getTheme()` - Get current theme (Dark/Light)
- `insertTextIntoChatInputBox(text)` - Insert text into chat
- `copyWithToast(text, toastMessage?)` - Copy to clipboard with toast
- `sendMessage(channelId, data, waitForChannelReady?, options?)` - Send message
- `openImageModal(item, mediaModalProps?)` - Open image modal
- `openUserProfile(id)` - Open user profile modal
- `fetchUserProfile(id, options?, cache?)` - Fetch user profile
- `getUniqueUsername(user)` - Get unique username (handles pomelo)
- `getEmojiURL(id, animated, size)` - Get emoji URL (always GIF for animated)
- `getGuildAcronym(guild)` - Get guild acronym
- `hasGuildFeature(guild, feature)` - Check guild feature

**DO NOT**: Directly use Discord webpack modules for these operations

```typescript
import { getCurrentChannel, sendMessage, copyWithToast } from "@utils/discord";

const channel = getCurrentChannel();
await sendMessage(channel.id, { content: "Hello!" });
await copyWithToast("Copied!", "Text copied to clipboard");
```

