### Text Utilities

**USE**: `text.ts` from `@utils/text`

**Available functions:**
- `wordsFromCamel(text)` - Convert camelCase to words
- `wordsFromSnake(text)` - Convert snake_case to words
- `wordsFromKebab(text)` - Convert kebab-case to words
- `wordsFromPascal(text)` - Convert PascalCase to words
- `wordsFromTitle(text)` - Convert Title Case to words
- `wordsToCamel(words)` - Convert words to camelCase
- `wordsToSnake(words)` - Convert words to SNAKE_CASE
- `wordsToKebab(words)` - Convert words to kebab-case
- `wordsToPascal(words)` - Convert words to PascalCase
- `wordsToTitle(words)` - Convert words to Title Case
- `formatDuration(time, unit, short?)` - Format duration (e.g., "1 day, 2 hours")
- `formatDurationMs(ms, human?, seconds?)` - Format milliseconds
- `humanFriendlyJoin(elements, mapper?)` - Join array with "and" (e.g., "1, 2 and 3")
- `makeCodeblock(text, language?)` - Wrap text in code block
- `stripIndent(strings, ...values)` - Strip indentation from template strings
- `toInlineCode(s)` - Convert to inline code with zero-width spaces
- `ZWSP` - Zero-width space constant

**DO NOT**: Create custom text transformation functions

```typescript
import { formatDuration, humanFriendlyJoin, makeCodeblock } from "@utils/text";

const duration = formatDuration(1, "days", false); // "1 day"
const joined = humanFriendlyJoin(["apple", "banana", "cherry"]); // "apple, banana and cherry"
const code = makeCodeblock("const x = 1;", "javascript");
```

