### Queue

**USE**: `Queue` class from `@utils/Queue`

**DO NOT**: Create custom queue implementations for sequential tasks

```typescript
import { Queue } from "@utils/Queue";

const queue = new Queue(10); // Max 10 items
queue.push(async () => {
    // Task 1
});
queue.push(async () => {
    // Task 2 (runs after task 1)
});
queue.unshift(async () => {
    // Task 0 (runs next, before task 1)
});
```

